cs.FL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with fuzzy finite automata and their determinization methods. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as fuzzy logic is used in the paper. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses algorithms for determinization and state reduction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is possible as fuzzy logic is often used in AI applications. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses automata and their reduction, which can be relevant to programming language theory.
